**Prerequisites**

Installations

Code Editor - Visual Studio code [Download](https://code.visualstudio.com/download) supports every operating systems too

Terraform - Please download here Terraform [Download](https://www.terraform.io/downloads)

Docker - To build the Docker image, you can use Docker Desktop for Windows or MacOS. [Docker Desktop Download](https://www.docker.com/products/docker-desktop)

Azure setup - To follow along with this tutorial, you should have an Azure account. If you don't already have one, you can sign up for a free 12 month trial here. [Azure Sign up](https://azure.microsoft.com/en-gb/free/)